      "message": "LGTM % s/branch/ref in proto.\n\nBy the way, I\u0027ve been wondering, why do you need this API?\nThere is already existing Gitiles API in https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/common/proto/gitiles/gitiles.proto?q\u003dluci%20proto%20gitiles",
